    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the macaroni is cooking, add the <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>chicken bites </strong>to a large bowl with<strong> </strong>half <span class=\"text-danger\">[all]</span><strong> </strong>the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 2? Save the remaining natural yoghurt for another recipe!</p><p>Add the <strong>ground paprika</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>garam masala</strong>, a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up, then set aside – this is your <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>chicken tikka</strong></p>",
